data.text:
Living large and living life, Hollywood style. We’re rounding up the latest in celeb lifestyle news with POP TALK! Welcome to the celebrity life!

H O M E S

Halle Berry Lists Malibu Mansion

Halle Berry is looking for a buyer for her Malibu mansion. The ‘Catwoman’ star has listed her purr-fect 3-br, 5-bath property for $18M. The home has over 5,000 sq ft of living space and is located in the gated community of Malibu Cove Colony.

R E L A T I O N S H I P S

PARENTHOOD: Jane Kramer & Allan Russell

Jana Kramer has welcomed her third child. The 39-year-old country singer has given birth to a baby boy with her fiancé Allan Russell. The happy parents have revealed their son’s name: Roman James Russell. The little one is Jana’s first child with Allan.
